        <abstract>
            <p>His admiration for HF’s paper on American fossil elephant.</p>
            <p>Notes "temporary irruption of S. American forms into N. America".</p> 
<p>Rejoices that HF has "smashed" case of <hi rend="italic">Mastodon</hi> on Timor.</p> 
            <p>Shares HF’s anger at Owen.</p> 
<p>He is eager to hear about fossil bird [<hi rend="italic">Archaeopteryx</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Comments on criticisms of species theory by [Johann Andreas?] Wagner.</p>
            <p>Describes research on fertilisation of Melastomataceae.</p>
        </abstract>
